You will need to do this in the code, rather than in the rich text editor tools.

&lt;a href="{{personalization.token.code.for.url}}&gt;Whatever text you want it to be&lt;/a&gt;

You can also go a step further and use &lt;a href="{{personalization.token.code}}&gt;{{personalization.token.for.name}}&lt;/a&gt;

Let me know if a video would be helpful. :slightly_smiling_face:
